漏洞信息漏洞名称： Fortinet SSL-VPN 堆缓冲区溢出漏洞 漏洞编号： CVE： CVE-2022-42475 漏洞类型： 缓冲区溢出 漏洞等级： 严重 漏洞描述： Fortinet SSL-VPN中存在一个堆缓冲区溢出漏洞（CWE-122），影响FortiOS（版本7.2.0至7.2.2、7.0.0至7.0.8、6.4.0至6.4.10、6.2.0至6.2.11、6.0.15及更早版本）和FortiProxy SSL-VPN（版本7.2.0至7.2.1、7.0.7及更早版本）。远程未认证攻击者可通过特制请求执行任意代码或命令。 产品厂商： fortinet 产品名称： fortios 影响版本： 7.2.0 &lt;&#x3D; version &lt;&#x3D; 7.2.2, 7.0.0 &lt;&#x3D; version &lt;&#x3D; 7.0.8, 6.4.0 &lt;&#x3D; version &lt;&#x3D; 6.4.10, 6.2.0 &lt;&#x3D; version &lt;&#x3D; 6.2.11, version &lt;&#x3D; 6.0.15 搜索语法： port:10443 http.favicon.hash:945408572, cpe:”cpe:2.3:o:fortinet:fortios”, http.html:”&#x2F;remote&#x2F;login” “xxxxxxxx” 来源： https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/31a500df8d7088e356de44763829f90209a17495/code%2Fcves%2F2022%2FCVE-2022-42475.yaml 类型： projectdiscovery&#x2F;nuclei-templates:github issues POC详情: CVE-2024-42475info: name: Heap-based Buffer Overflow in Fortinet SSL-VPN author: 0xhaggis, pszyszkowski severity: critical description: | A heap-based buffer overflow vulnerability [CWE-122] in FortiOS SSL-VPN (versions 7.2.0 through 7.2.2, 7.0.0 through 7.0.8, 6.4.0 through 6.4.10, 6.2.0 through 6.2.11, 6.0.15 and earlier) and FortiProxy SSL-VPN (versions 7.2.0 through 7.2.1, 7.0.7 and earlier) may allow a remote unauthenticated attacker to execute arbitrary code or commands via specifically crafted requests. remediation: | Fixed in: FortiOS &gt;= 7.2.3, 7.0.9, 6.4.11, 6.2.12, 6.0.16 FortiOS-6K7K &gt;= 7.0.8, 6.4.10, 6.2.12, 6.0.15 FortiProxy &gt;= 7.2.2, 7.0.8, 2.0.12 reference: - https://github.com/0xhaggis/CVE-2022-42475 - https://github.com/CKevens/CVE-2022-42475-RCE-POC - https://github.com/Amir-hy/cve-2022-42475 - https://github.com/Mustafa1986/cve-2022-42475-Fortinet - https://github.com/natceil/cve-2022-42475 - https://github.com/scrt/cve-2022-42475 - https://fortiguard.com/psirt/FG-IR-22-398 - https://labs.watchtowr.com/fortinet-no-more-funny-titles-cve-2022-42475/ - https://bishopfox.com/blog/exploit-cve-2022-42475 classificati